      ],
      "research_type": "mixed",
      "paper_scope": "Collect literature data on physical properties of steels to build a database, analyze the influence of composition on the elastic modulus of steels divided into three groups (martensitic + ferritic steels, ferritic steels, austenitic steels), perform thermodynamic analysis with Thermo-Calc for ferritic and austenitic steels, carry out regression analysis to obtain the influence coefficients of components on elastic modulus, which can be used to predict the elastic modulus of steels with known composition."
    }
